metadata.name: Calculating
metadata.description:
Osita Iheme is an actor who has appeared in over 100 movies, and is best known for his role as "Paw-Paw" in the Aki and Paw-Paw series of Nigerian comedy films. Clips from the films featuring Osita have been turned into numerous memes that have been shared around the world, turning Osita into a bonafide meme superstar. His rise to viral fame began in 2019 when rapper 50 Cent posted Osita's "Calculating" meme. This set off a wave of Osita memes being used by various celebrities and media sites including; Snoop Dogg, Genius, Complex Sports, Bitcoin Magazine, E! News, and Fenty Beauty among many others.

This 1/1 authenticated NFT is offered by Osita himself, and will grant its holder a lifetime of enjoyment.
